{"tid":1693391,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"（全球罷食初步成功）英國連鎖餐廳Pizza Express陷財困 又一中資持股「水土不服」？","createTime":"2019-11-04T14:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:13:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f13ce23d0599cd2fbd6a17e16532ffa5734da171","tid":1693391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"再有老牌英國企業出事，薄餅連鎖店Pizza Express，正面臨6.65億英鎊（約64億港元）債款恐無法償還。盡管Pizza Express目前情況未到英國老牌旅遊公司Thomas Cook突然宣布破產的絕境，惟兩者相同的是背後大股東均是中資企業，這是否反映中資持股的海外企業容易「水土不服」？<br />\n<br />\n債台高築的Pizza Express有逾50年歷史，於英國頗有名，據彭博報道Pizza Express面臨兩筆合共6.65億英鎊債款，分別於2021及2022年到期。報道稱Pizza Express的債務重組已刻不容緩，目前正於與債權人作初期談判，並聘請了顧問。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>聯控旗下弘毅投資2014年全購Pizza Express</strong><br />\n<br />\n雖然Pizza Express是傳統英國餐廳，惟背後母公司為中資企業。聯想控股 （03396） 旗下的弘毅投資於2014年，以作價9億英鎊（約86億港元）全購Pizza Express，當時是歐洲過去5年最大宗的餐飲業併購案。值得一值，Pizza Express除了以上的對外6.65億英鎊債務，還欠5億英鎊為母公司弘毅投資的股東貸款。<br />\n<br />\nPizza Express面臨財困受英國人關注，盡管Pizza Express未到Thomas Cook破產的絕境，惟百年老店Thomas Cook突然結業，令不少英國人感惋惜，為免Pizza Express重蹈Thomas Cook的覆轍，有人甚至發起「拯救Pizza Express」的運動。<br />\n<br />\nSource: hket"},{"pid":"7da3efd5894a48c18af56bb679347d8f97ac5eaf","tid":1693391,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"Btw琴日經過新城市嗰間, 見到長長嘅人龍...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人記得呢間要罷食啦"},{"pid":"f2e3bc5e16767600773af64e4441bc1c2637799d","tid":1693391,"uid":277114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63d116ae7ed8c8659e4332e5a68d9a61055a1220","tid":1693391,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"又唔覺喎，<br />\n平時見都仲有人幫襯㗎。"},{"pid":"7b7682dbdaad045f614f4902e9a9ca05d9d81327","tid":1693391,"uid":266676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63d116ae7ed8c8659e4332e5a68d9a61055a1220","tid":1693391,"uid":58147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:47:28.000Z","msg":"又唔覺喎，<br />\n平時見都仲有人幫襯㗎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"有人幫襯同冇錢還係2樣野"},{"pid":"b75a2dacdebc05c68d37c90579ae68b64c709084","tid":1693391,"uid":326032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"究竟係因為管理不善先會俾中資食住，定係中資搞到佢地有營業困難？"},{"pid":"654cc481be54a3e2dfb194bfc5de3b47da026b2c","tid":1693391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b75a2dacdebc05c68d37c90579ae68b64c709084","tid":1693391,"uid":326032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"究竟係因為管理不善先會俾中資食住，定係中資搞到佢地有營業困難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"係因為全球罷食"},{"pid":"c15658d60c8d9be0a118e9cfd5b677bf5b2b94ee","tid":1693391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc762d6f76ce0027e91fe4091a6406182a0b49d9","tid":1693391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af372d718656de23be16646fcd7bf02cd2133ea4","tid":1693391,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"罷食"},{"pid":"43b7ff306e254b6f6f9df484521e3f611c7e5e5d","tid":1693391,"uid":268516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b75a2dacdebc05c68d37c90579ae68b64c709084","tid":1693391,"uid":326032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:59:54.000Z","msg":"究竟係因為管理不善先會俾中資食住，定係中資搞到佢地有營業困難？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"不過盤生意肯賣俾人，應該都係因為睇到高位已過"},{"pid":"d64acc966ea5edfcc6b6445e48dd5617bc838bfa","tid":1693391,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}